Nightlife in Lagos and other parts of the country may never remain the same again as Folixx Bukka, popular night life club is set to redefine social life in style. With new directors sucg as Nigerian music ace, Oluseyi Sheyman Ademoye, Olugbenga Sunday Awe and Aliu Lakaban Bambgola joining forces together to take over the the affairs of the club and turning its fortune around. It will be recalled that Sheyman, who has been running the club for sometime has now teamed up with new partners as they looked set to restore the glory of Folixx Bukka and keep it running smoothly. Why Army is diversifying —Buratai More trouble for Nigeria as crude price crashes to $46.31/b The Power of a Book I was a pickpocket before I found God —Mike Bamiloye Speaking with our reporter on the next step, Sheyman disclosed that the partnership would give birth to innovations that would make the place people’s favourite, especially those who place value on nightlife events. Located at Lekki in Lagos State, the place will now run a 24-hour service delivery to the public with classy and tasteful ambience and services. He added that a new record label would also spring up as part of the new partnership, adding that a new luxury adult club Secrets would be unveiled soon. Sheyman, a prolific songwriter and music producer was famed with hit tracks such Hotter Than Fire, Shampuwa among others. Abuja woman reveals natural remedy for Diabetes and solution to balance blood sugar level within few weeks without  insulin or drugs! HERE IS HOW OVER 5000  NIGERIA MEN HAVE PERMANENTLY OVERCOME TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS RECENT DISCOVERY BY MEDICAL CONSULTANTS LOOK!  YOU DONT NEED TO HAVE ANY EXPERIENCE TO TRADE ONLINE,WE WILL DO IT ALL FOR YOU AND YOU WILL START EARNING A LIVING FROM TRADING ONLINE TODAY AND PROFITS WILL BE PAID TO YOUR ACCOUNT DIRECTLY. CLICK HERE TO REGISTER AND EARN